WEBVTT

01:51.860 --> 01:57.410
[The Legend of Rosy Clouds]

01:58.560 --> 02:01.920
[Episode 24]

02:02.500 --> 02:04.440
The Spirit Immortal comes forth.

02:04.980 --> 02:07.040
The people are saved from disasters.

02:07.680 --> 02:09.570
The holy sect descends.

02:10.120 --> 02:12.310
The sun and moon shine again.

02:15.520 --> 02:18.180
Shouldn't we investigate
the mass grave first?

02:18.329 --> 02:20.650
These two things must be connected.

02:20.670 --> 02:22.829
I've asked Gao Ran to look for Desheng.

02:23.000 --> 02:25.460
Let's see if we can find
any clues here first.

02:25.740 --> 02:26.670
Okay.

02:31.160 --> 02:33.530
The Spirit Immortal comes forth.

02:33.560 --> 02:35.840
The people are saved from disasters.

02:36.290 --> 02:38.100
The holy sect descends.

02:38.620 --> 02:40.820
The sun and moon shine again.

02:49.430 --> 02:51.460
Everything comes with a price.

02:51.920 --> 02:54.890
If you want true salvation,

02:55.120 --> 02:58.680
you must show
the Spirit Immortal your sincerity.

02:59.000 --> 03:00.770
As long as you can save my child,

03:00.790 --> 03:02.820
I am willing to serve the Spirit Immortal
for the rest of my life.

03:02.820 --> 03:04.520
I would be your humble servant forever.

03:04.520 --> 03:06.710
-Yes, be your humble servant forever!
-Be your humble servant forever!

03:06.710 --> 03:09.310
-I'm willing!
-Be your humble servant forever!

03:09.310 --> 03:12.120
-I'm willing!
-Be your humble servant forever!

03:40.430 --> 03:42.950
This must be a miracle! It's incredible!

03:44.630 --> 03:46.540
-Unbelievable!
-Yes!

03:48.470 --> 03:49.880
Have you all seen that?

03:50.420 --> 03:52.140
The Spirit Immortal has ordered

03:52.140 --> 03:54.100
that if the witch Fan Yun dies,

03:54.240 --> 03:56.430
your sins will be forgiven.

03:56.880 --> 03:59.280
Fan Yun? It's Fan Yun again!

03:59.310 --> 04:01.150
How long is she going to plague us?

04:01.150 --> 04:03.270
-Kill her!
-Kill her!

04:03.300 --> 04:04.690
Let's go.

04:04.910 --> 04:07.080
-Kill her!
-Kill her!

04:07.080 --> 04:08.190
The witch is here!

04:08.190 --> 04:10.150
Folks, the witch is right here!

04:10.150 --> 04:11.430
She is Fan Yun!

04:11.510 --> 04:13.640
Where are you going? You can't escape!

04:14.080 --> 04:14.890
Fan Yun,

04:14.920 --> 04:16.720
you are the origin of the plague.

04:17.010 --> 04:18.390
My son took your medicine,

04:18.390 --> 04:20.029
and he is still unconscious!

04:20.060 --> 04:22.060
She is also the one who killed my son!

04:22.110 --> 04:23.440
What did I say back then?

04:23.510 --> 04:25.120
We shouldn't have let them into the city!

04:25.120 --> 04:26.030
You didn't believe me.

04:26.030 --> 04:28.090
Now the truth is right in front of you!

04:28.160 --> 04:28.780
Kill her!

04:36.090 --> 04:37.180
Hurry!

04:39.950 --> 04:40.630
This way!

04:49.770 --> 04:50.420
Come!

04:54.120 --> 04:55.300
Go that way! Go!

04:57.510 --> 04:58.180
Here!

05:03.990 --> 05:08.990
-Open the door!
-Come out quickly!

05:09.020 --> 05:11.100
Open the door!

05:11.120 --> 05:17.920
-Open the door!
-Come out quickly!

05:17.950 --> 05:18.670
I'll go over there.

05:18.670 --> 05:19.380
Okay.

05:30.870 --> 05:32.340
Fang can't make it either!

05:32.370 --> 05:33.780
Burn them to death!

05:33.800 --> 05:36.630
-Burn them to death!
-Burn them to death!

05:39.630 --> 05:41.020
Seems we've fallen into a trap.

05:41.020 --> 05:42.710
The Spirit Immortal Sect
doesn't want to save them at all,

05:42.710 --> 05:43.710
but to incite them

05:43.740 --> 05:44.850
to take your life together.

05:44.850 --> 05:47.000
Yes, but we've found out

05:47.030 --> 05:48.000
too late.

05:48.020 --> 05:51.460
-Burn them to death!
-Burn them to death!

06:12.240 --> 06:14.360
Yong City is in chaos right now.

06:14.380 --> 06:15.970
The brewers are in no mood to brew.

06:15.970 --> 06:17.970
These vessels are really cheap.

06:18.650 --> 06:21.670
If I ship them back to Ling'an,
the price will at least triple.

06:21.670 --> 06:23.890
Juyun Pavilion
has really got a knack for it.

06:23.890 --> 06:24.600
Boss.

06:24.620 --> 06:26.460
Someone said they took
Miss Fan's sweet wormwood prescription

06:26.460 --> 06:27.610
and died of poisoning.

06:27.610 --> 06:28.510
They are on the street right now.

06:28.510 --> 06:30.590
I've checked the goods. No problem.

06:31.470 --> 06:33.610
Go get the money
we've made these past few days.

06:33.610 --> 06:34.240
Yes.

06:38.330 --> 06:40.060
He's really here to make money.

06:57.950 --> 06:58.830
This is bad!

06:58.850 --> 07:00.310
They've really set a fire.

07:06.550 --> 07:07.280
Come with me.

07:15.450 --> 07:16.640
This way.

07:17.190 --> 07:23.110
-Burn her!
-Burn her!

07:23.140 --> 07:24.750
What do we do now?

07:24.770 --> 07:29.770
-Burn her!
-Burn her!

07:29.800 --> 07:30.900
We have to quickly figure out a way

07:30.900 --> 07:32.159
to get the message out.

08:28.310 --> 08:29.240
Are you alright?

08:30.290 --> 08:30.810
Come.

08:57.590 --> 08:58.510
Fan Yun.

09:00.270 --> 09:01.030
Since our lives

09:01.030 --> 09:02.690
are already in others' hands,

09:03.720 --> 09:05.000
maybe we will be saved,

09:06.170 --> 09:06.960
or maybe this

09:06.960 --> 09:08.690
is the last moment of our lives.

09:09.840 --> 09:11.130
If so,

09:11.810 --> 09:13.320
let's not waste it.

09:19.480 --> 09:20.410
I...

09:21.960 --> 09:22.960
Your Excellency,

09:23.440 --> 09:24.440
then...

09:25.180 --> 09:26.940
what do you want to do?

09:28.100 --> 09:29.150
I want to...

09:31.560 --> 09:33.280
-I don't want...
-I want...

09:34.090 --> 09:35.620
to listen to you play a song.

09:39.810 --> 09:41.210
At a time like this,

09:41.240 --> 09:43.100
you still want to listen to a song?

09:52.120 --> 09:53.270
What is this drawing?

09:53.270 --> 09:54.530
Can you understand it?

09:56.080 --> 09:57.620
We can't understand what you drew.

09:57.620 --> 09:58.980
It should be here.

10:16.740 --> 10:18.340
Take the goods and follow me.

10:23.940 --> 10:24.700
Keep up!

10:56.960 --> 10:58.290
I'll go pour some water.

11:01.940 --> 11:03.270
Here, Your Excellency.

11:03.690 --> 11:05.080
Cover your mouth and nose with this.

11:05.080 --> 11:06.610
It'll make you feel better.

11:08.790 --> 11:09.630
I...

11:11.350 --> 11:12.190
Fan Yun.

11:13.870 --> 11:15.800
I won't let anything happen to you.

11:30.410 --> 11:31.570
Don't worry.

11:33.030 --> 11:35.000
We will definitely get out safely.

11:37.240 --> 11:38.840
If anything happens to you,

11:39.940 --> 11:42.150
I will be a windower
for the rest of my life.

11:42.150 --> 11:42.910
Win...

11:45.410 --> 11:46.340
Windower?

11:46.940 --> 11:48.670
What do you mean by "windower"?

11:52.150 --> 11:53.430
I heard from Lord Lyu

11:54.680 --> 11:57.410
that this is how commoners
refer to being single.

12:01.720 --> 12:02.630
Silly.

12:03.360 --> 12:04.880
It's not called that.

12:04.910 --> 12:06.170
It's called a widower.

12:06.480 --> 12:07.390
Besides,

12:07.910 --> 12:10.110
a widower doesn't necessarily mean...

12:45.460 --> 12:48.600
♪ Watch how many flowers
bloom and wither ♪

12:49.020 --> 12:52.450
♪ Count how many springs
and autumns pass ♪

12:52.820 --> 12:55.380
♪ Why the sighs and regrets? ♪

13:01.440 --> 13:04.930
♪ Lovers wait a lifetime ♪

13:05.400 --> 13:08.600
♪ Feelings that can't be severed ♪

13:09.020 --> 13:11.770
♪ How to let go? ♪

13:23.630 --> 13:24.230
Move!

13:24.250 --> 13:25.300
Move!

13:25.330 --> 13:26.370
Save them!

13:26.390 --> 13:27.540
Stop them!

13:27.570 --> 13:29.630
Let's see who dares to save the witch.

13:29.750 --> 13:31.080
I don't care who you are.

13:31.540 --> 13:33.070
Arrest them all!

13:34.650 --> 13:36.580
It seems someone is here to save us.

13:36.630 --> 13:37.430
I'll go check.

13:40.120 --> 13:41.080
Bring him up!

13:43.710 --> 13:44.870
It's Lou Qiyan!

13:44.890 --> 13:46.220
There is hope for us!

14:07.060 --> 14:08.380
This is the man

14:08.410 --> 14:09.940
who roamed around Yong City

14:09.950 --> 14:11.570
and switched Lady Fan Yun's medicine.

14:11.570 --> 14:12.850
I was forced to do it!

14:12.910 --> 14:13.370
I...

14:13.580 --> 14:15.030
-I...
-Did you hear that?

14:15.060 --> 14:16.900
He said he was forced.

14:16.960 --> 14:18.360
Why should I believe you?

14:18.680 --> 14:19.350
A few days ago,

14:19.350 --> 14:20.820
I did see him at my door.

14:20.850 --> 14:21.850
I really saw him.

14:21.870 --> 14:22.830
I saw him too.

14:22.870 --> 14:24.390
I also saw them at my door.

14:25.490 --> 14:27.060
His Excellency is our witness.

14:27.060 --> 14:29.160
Since Lady Fan Yun brought
sweet wormwood to save people,

14:29.160 --> 14:31.550
why would she use poisonous medicine
to harm them?

14:31.550 --> 14:32.300
Obviously,

14:32.590 --> 14:35.120
the decoction your family took
was poisoned.

14:35.400 --> 14:37.160
I believe you all know

14:37.190 --> 14:39.470
who benefits from this.

14:41.880 --> 14:43.910
I don't believe either of you.

14:44.280 --> 14:45.680
My son is lying in bed now,

14:45.710 --> 14:47.770
and I don't know if he will live or die!

14:47.960 --> 14:49.410
I have made my reasoning clear.

14:49.410 --> 14:51.270
It's up to you whether you believe me.

14:51.270 --> 14:53.800
If anyone dares to stop me
from saving them today,

14:53.800 --> 14:55.660
you'll have to deal with me first.

14:56.510 --> 14:58.840
Get out of the way! Protect the civilians!

14:59.810 --> 15:01.640
Put out the fire! Quick!

15:48.060 --> 15:50.660
I didn't expect
that after coming to Yong City,

15:50.800 --> 15:53.600
I still wouldn't be able
to control my own destiny.

15:54.680 --> 15:56.590
If I really die here today,

15:58.050 --> 15:59.480
what a pity it would be.

16:00.150 --> 16:01.150
Your Excellency.

16:01.460 --> 16:02.940
We need to be optimistic.

16:03.840 --> 16:04.910
We must believe

16:05.130 --> 16:06.360
that Gao Ran and the others

16:06.360 --> 16:07.660
will definitely rush over

16:07.660 --> 16:08.970
to rescue us.

16:11.450 --> 16:12.480
Besides,

16:14.300 --> 16:15.850
we must get out.

16:16.520 --> 16:17.810
My father and Gao Ran

16:17.840 --> 16:19.640
are still waiting for me at home.

16:20.800 --> 16:22.590
I can't die here.

16:35.070 --> 16:36.730
Sometimes, I really hate you.

16:40.270 --> 16:41.980
You never think about me,

16:43.050 --> 16:45.050
and you don't understand men at all.

16:46.250 --> 16:47.890
Besides me in this world,

16:49.000 --> 16:50.930
no one else would want to marry you.

16:55.890 --> 16:57.460
I'm sorry, Your Excellency,

16:57.460 --> 16:59.380
I didn't mean to say that.

17:01.420 --> 17:02.660
How about this?

17:03.600 --> 17:04.970
When we leave here safely

17:04.970 --> 17:05.970
and get out,

17:05.990 --> 17:08.390
I'll make a big table
of your favorite food.

17:08.670 --> 17:09.560
How's that?

17:14.510 --> 17:16.060
Then I don't want any radish in it.

17:16.060 --> 17:17.650
But radish is cheap.

17:20.270 --> 17:21.589
All right. All right.

17:21.619 --> 17:22.650
I'll listen to you today.

17:22.400 --> 17:23.869
♪ I could have ♪

17:23.900 --> 17:25.490
♪ Played every trick in the book ♪

17:25.520 --> 17:28.880
♪ But I chose painstaking devotion ♪

17:26.069 --> 17:28.730
I want to listen to you
play the erhu all the time.

17:29.060 --> 17:30.710
♪ Never caging my love ♪

17:30.440 --> 17:31.000
Okay.

17:30.740 --> 17:34.960
♪ Even if I had to
trudge through a thousand miles ♪

17:31.000 --> 17:32.200
Take a walk together.

17:33.150 --> 17:34.320
Okay.

17:34.340 --> 17:35.610
Plant a phoenix tree together.

17:35.090 --> 17:39.160
♪ Henceforth, I shall wander the world,
plucking petals and holding the moon ♪

17:36.880 --> 17:37.550
Okay.

17:37.550 --> 17:38.780
Admire the moon together.

17:38.780 --> 17:39.450
Okay.

17:39.420 --> 17:42.740
♪ Listen to the wind and admire the moon
for days on end ♪

17:39.480 --> 17:40.510
Wait for the sunrise together.

17:40.510 --> 17:40.830
Okay.

17:40.830 --> 17:41.680
Watch the sunrise together.

17:41.680 --> 17:42.400
Okay.

17:42.910 --> 17:48.840
♪ Accept that I'm not your happiness ♪

17:43.360 --> 17:44.230
Marry me.

17:46.300 --> 17:47.300
No.

17:48.910 --> 17:51.630
♪ Let go of what's before me ♪

17:50.790 --> 17:51.750
Why?

17:51.650 --> 17:55.610
♪ Consider this the best ending ♪

17:53.590 --> 17:55.830
Lady Fan, why is your heartbeat so fast?

17:55.730 --> 17:58.210
♪ I disdain everything
in the vast universe ♪

17:57.400 --> 17:59.310
Perhaps you were frightened by the fire.

17:58.240 --> 18:02.590
♪ So why do I care for
a single glance from you? ♪

18:00.030 --> 18:02.790
I will prescribe some medicine
for you to take,

18:02.620 --> 18:05.250
♪ Drinking a pot of the past ♪

18:02.790 --> 18:04.680
and you will recover
after resting for some days.

18:04.680 --> 18:05.440
Thank you.

18:05.270 --> 18:10.130
♪ I toast to my withering self
as the curtains fall ♪

18:06.240 --> 18:07.030
By the way,

18:07.030 --> 18:09.350
how are the people

18:09.350 --> 18:10.590
who took the fake medicine?

18:10.150 --> 18:16.380
♪ And you don't know the reason why ♪

18:10.590 --> 18:13.070
I've sent people to help replace it
with the real medicine.

18:13.070 --> 18:14.510
For those who took the fake medicine,

18:14.510 --> 18:15.400
we are trying our best to use some

18:15.400 --> 18:17.700
emetic prescriptions
to clear their stomachs.

18:17.700 --> 18:26.360
♪ And you don't know the reason why ♪

18:18.340 --> 18:19.940
Thank you for your hard work.

18:20.780 --> 18:21.650
It's my duty.

18:24.390 --> 18:25.840
I will take my leave.

18:36.350 --> 18:37.680
I told you I was perfectly healthy,

18:37.680 --> 18:38.520
and I'm fine.

18:38.550 --> 18:40.280
But you insisted I see a doctor.

18:40.470 --> 18:41.830
You stayed in the fire for a long time,

18:41.830 --> 18:43.520
and you must have inhaled
some toxic fumes.

18:43.520 --> 18:45.680
It's good to let a physician take a look.

18:45.680 --> 18:47.280
How is His Excellency doing?

18:49.350 --> 18:50.350
After he's back,

18:50.640 --> 18:53.100
-he's been resting in the room.
-Put it here.

18:56.550 --> 18:57.720
I'm glad he's fine.

19:00.680 --> 19:01.540
Today,

19:02.000 --> 19:03.500
thank you for showing up in time.

19:03.500 --> 19:05.250
And thank you for your refinement vessels,

19:05.250 --> 19:06.780
which really helped us out.

19:09.320 --> 19:10.920
Boss, these things

19:10.950 --> 19:12.950
can't be used to make money anymore.

19:23.000 --> 19:24.200
Originally, these vessels

19:24.200 --> 19:25.000
were collected

19:25.000 --> 19:27.310
to sell to Ling'an wine merchants
for making wine.

19:27.310 --> 19:29.030
But since the refinement vessels
among them

19:29.030 --> 19:31.030
can speed up your medicine-making,

19:31.480 --> 19:32.510
I'll do you a favor

19:32.510 --> 19:34.090
and sell them to His Excellency.

19:34.090 --> 19:36.880
I also promised my subordinates
to make some money.

19:36.880 --> 19:37.990
Anyway,

19:38.590 --> 19:39.720
thank you.

19:40.160 --> 19:41.140
But don't worry,

19:41.720 --> 19:42.720
we

19:43.140 --> 19:45.380
won't let you make a loss.

19:49.670 --> 19:51.870
You don't need to thank me on his behalf.

19:52.550 --> 19:53.270
However,

19:54.090 --> 19:55.750
if you really want to thank me,

19:58.180 --> 19:59.530
you might as well consider resigning

19:59.530 --> 20:00.730
and leaving Qi Zheng.

20:01.290 --> 20:02.490
The world is vast,

20:02.520 --> 20:05.450
and you won't be involved
with the Qi family anymore.

20:08.850 --> 20:10.200
Then I won't be polite.

20:12.070 --> 20:13.000
You have already felt

20:13.000 --> 20:14.920
the disrespect from the common people.

20:14.920 --> 20:17.750
As long as you stay by Qi Zheng's side
as an official,

20:17.750 --> 20:18.960
the difficulties you will face

20:18.960 --> 20:20.110
and the danger he brings to you

20:20.110 --> 20:21.350
will only increase.

20:21.810 --> 20:22.680
No.

20:23.870 --> 20:24.980
He won't hurt me.

20:25.110 --> 20:26.530
He is the governor of the Nine Cities.

20:26.530 --> 20:29.330
If he has to choose
between the Nine Cities and you,

20:31.730 --> 20:34.530
he will only choose the Nine Cities
and give you up.

20:36.120 --> 20:38.120
That's exactly what I want him to do.

20:40.720 --> 20:41.590
Fan Yun.

20:42.950 --> 20:44.080
If it were me,

20:44.100 --> 20:45.140
I wouldn't.

20:47.410 --> 20:50.010
Because you are more important
than the world.

21:09.640 --> 21:10.600
If...

21:12.990 --> 21:15.450
if you're talking about romantic feelings,

21:16.400 --> 21:19.060
I only regard you
as a good friend and confidant.

21:20.740 --> 21:23.130
If you're talking about
my official career,

21:23.130 --> 21:24.770
this is the path I chose.

21:25.790 --> 21:27.240
I have to walk it myself.

21:35.310 --> 21:36.400
It's fine.

21:36.660 --> 21:37.900
We businessmen

21:37.930 --> 21:39.250
are the most patient.

23:07.000 --> 23:08.000
Your Excellency!

23:08.500 --> 23:10.090
Your Excellency, Lady Fan Yun.

23:10.090 --> 23:10.950
I've found out.

23:11.480 --> 23:13.400
The dead people in the mass grave

23:13.430 --> 23:14.920
were those from the village

23:14.920 --> 23:17.850
who believed in the Spirit Immortal Sect
a while ago.

23:18.290 --> 23:19.570
But these people

23:19.600 --> 23:20.810
ruined their families to join the sect.

23:20.810 --> 23:22.160
Why is there no record

23:22.190 --> 23:23.350
in the files?

23:25.650 --> 23:26.860
Y-Your Excellency,

23:26.890 --> 23:28.240
L-Lady Fan Yun,

23:28.260 --> 23:30.740
a-as to the Spirit Immortal Sect,

23:30.880 --> 23:32.240
in Yong City,

23:32.260 --> 23:34.750
there have always been many commoners

23:34.920 --> 23:36.440
joining and believing in it.

23:36.440 --> 23:37.960
During this plague,

23:37.980 --> 23:39.460
it's imperative

23:40.060 --> 23:42.190
to prioritize fighting the epidemic.

23:51.350 --> 23:52.500
Hurry, bring him up!

23:55.020 --> 23:56.020
Your Excellency,

23:56.060 --> 23:57.060
Lady Fan Yun,

23:57.090 --> 23:59.300
there's still a survivor
in the mass grave!

23:59.300 --> 24:00.560
Quick, bring him here!

24:09.430 --> 24:10.270
How is he?

24:10.560 --> 24:11.590
His pulse is weak.

24:11.610 --> 24:13.680
Someone probably thought
he was beyond saving

24:13.680 --> 24:15.440
and abandoned him here.

24:15.460 --> 24:16.820
Luckily, we found him in time.

24:16.820 --> 24:18.710
Otherwise, he wouldn't have
survived the night.

24:18.710 --> 24:20.310
Quick, give me the medicine.

24:30.480 --> 24:31.440
Don't be afraid.

24:31.640 --> 24:32.570
You're safe now.

24:33.110 --> 24:34.370
What do you want to say?

24:35.190 --> 24:36.920
It's the Spirit Immortal Sect.

24:37.000 --> 24:38.400
They are harming people.

24:41.400 --> 24:43.000
What happened with the sect?

24:43.520 --> 24:44.850
Those from the sect said

24:45.470 --> 24:46.840
if we joined,

24:46.860 --> 24:51.010
we would get the Spirit Immortal Water
to cure the plague for free.

24:51.110 --> 24:52.090
Who would've known

24:52.090 --> 24:55.000
that the Spirit Immortal Water
would be completely useless.

24:55.000 --> 24:56.860
It even worsened your condition,

24:57.050 --> 24:59.710
causing you to miss the best time
for treatment.

25:00.640 --> 25:01.480
We originally wanted

25:01.480 --> 25:03.320
to return to the city to seek a doctor,

25:03.320 --> 25:04.720
but they wouldn't let us.

25:06.890 --> 25:08.370
I feel so terrible.

25:09.250 --> 25:10.850
My family...

25:11.870 --> 25:14.660
All my family members are dead!

25:15.160 --> 25:16.200
Lie down first.

25:17.040 --> 25:19.610
Since the Spirit Immortal Sect
is doing such harm,

25:19.610 --> 25:21.010
they must be eradicated.

25:22.360 --> 25:22.920
Desheng.

25:23.500 --> 25:25.370
Send him to Zhu Luan's place
for treatment.

25:25.370 --> 25:26.060
Yes.

25:26.430 --> 25:27.080
Gao Ran,

25:27.480 --> 25:29.130
take a squad to escort them.

25:30.710 --> 25:31.520
Yes.

25:38.980 --> 25:40.840
Besides the people who died here,

25:41.080 --> 25:42.210
there must be other people

25:42.210 --> 25:43.480
deceived by the Spirit Immortal Sect

25:43.480 --> 25:45.280
who are dying one after another.

25:45.350 --> 25:46.740
We need to find them as soon as possible

25:46.740 --> 25:48.170
and treat them.

25:50.640 --> 25:53.200
The situation in Yong City
is complicated now.

25:53.200 --> 25:54.990
I don't know where Tian Xing and Suyin

25:54.990 --> 25:56.230
are right now.

25:57.090 --> 25:57.880
I hope

25:58.170 --> 25:59.890
they are safe.

26:08.610 --> 26:10.400
With such a large topographical map,

26:10.400 --> 26:12.340
how do we know exactly
which mountain it is?

26:12.340 --> 26:13.230
Yeah,

26:13.790 --> 26:14.960
where could it be?

26:16.790 --> 26:17.680
I found them!

26:18.440 --> 26:19.410
I found them!

26:19.800 --> 26:21.110
-Zhu Luan?
-Yun, I found them!

26:21.110 --> 26:22.370
Have some water first.

26:23.350 --> 26:24.190
Drink slowly.

26:26.360 --> 26:27.530
What did you find?

26:27.550 --> 26:29.870
I found Suyin and Brother.

26:29.900 --> 26:30.700
That's great.

26:40.910 --> 26:43.230
This is the topographical map
of the Spirit Immortal Sect.

26:43.230 --> 26:45.790
But the map seems a bit incomplete.

26:45.810 --> 26:46.770
Incomplete?

26:47.000 --> 26:47.460
Come on,

26:47.640 --> 26:48.770
tell me,

26:48.800 --> 26:49.950
how did you know

26:49.970 --> 26:51.620
which path to take?

26:51.650 --> 26:52.570
In the past,

26:52.590 --> 26:54.540
when Dad, Brother, and I

26:54.570 --> 26:56.110
went up the mountain to gather herbs,

26:56.110 --> 26:58.640
we found a shortcut to the cave.

26:58.720 --> 27:00.480
But the entrance is so small

27:00.500 --> 27:02.300
that adults can't get in.

27:02.440 --> 27:04.070
Only children can.

27:04.460 --> 27:05.870
After I went in,

27:05.890 --> 27:07.810
I saw many sick people.

27:08.090 --> 27:10.130
Suyin was taking care of them.

27:16.330 --> 27:17.880
In such a remote place,

27:17.910 --> 27:19.640
they must be short of medicine.

27:20.110 --> 27:20.880
Later,

27:20.880 --> 27:22.350
take some prepared medicine

27:22.350 --> 27:23.400
to Suyin.

27:25.270 --> 27:26.790
Suyin asked me to come back

27:26.790 --> 27:29.310
to fetch her some sweet wormwood.

27:29.800 --> 27:31.600
With so many people in distress,

27:31.640 --> 27:34.440
she definitely won't just
sit back and do nothing.

27:34.550 --> 27:36.070
The cave entrance you just mentioned—

27:36.070 --> 27:37.160
where is it?

27:38.640 --> 27:39.570
It's right here.

27:42.990 --> 27:43.880
Here.

27:44.790 --> 27:46.350
What we need to do next

27:46.370 --> 27:47.900
is to cooperate with Suyin.

27:51.920 --> 27:53.570
-Get up! Get up!
-Get up!

27:55.040 --> 27:55.880
Get up!

27:59.750 --> 28:01.210
Come on, bring your bowls.

28:07.460 --> 28:09.790
So many people every day!

28:09.810 --> 28:11.310
Why are there still
so many meals to deliver?

28:11.310 --> 28:13.040
There are still so many people!

28:13.440 --> 28:14.110
Come on, get up!

28:14.110 --> 28:15.640
Come on, everybody, get up!

28:16.590 --> 28:17.680
Actually, for lowly people like us,

28:17.680 --> 28:19.810
it's already good enough to have this.

28:19.920 --> 28:22.190
But you look so tired every day.

28:22.640 --> 28:24.730
At least you have some conscience,
little girl.

28:24.730 --> 28:25.850
With so many people,

28:25.850 --> 28:27.780
the two of us are almost exhausted!

28:28.550 --> 28:31.940
You're not trying to sweet-talk us

28:32.030 --> 28:33.690
into letting you out, are you?

28:34.000 --> 28:34.880
No way!

28:35.680 --> 28:37.060
You misunderstood me, Sir.

28:37.060 --> 28:38.540
I just wanted to say

28:38.570 --> 28:40.810
I can help you distribute the food

28:40.830 --> 28:42.550
to ease your burden.

28:42.640 --> 28:44.170
I have no other intentions.

28:44.320 --> 28:45.930
If the food is distributed late,

28:45.930 --> 28:48.330
some weak people
might get sick or die.

28:48.590 --> 28:50.500
Wouldn't that be more troublesome
to handle?

28:50.500 --> 28:51.980
If I can help you,

28:52.000 --> 28:53.730
it can save you time and effort.

28:53.810 --> 28:55.470
Besides, I'm just a weak woman,

28:55.470 --> 28:57.100
with so much food.

28:57.590 --> 29:00.250
You're not worried
you can't handle me, are you?

29:02.700 --> 29:03.550
Why don't we

29:03.570 --> 29:04.300
give it a try?

29:04.790 --> 29:06.410
I see her taking care
of people every time.

29:06.410 --> 29:07.740
She seems quite nimble.

29:08.680 --> 29:09.920
I'm warning you.

29:10.960 --> 29:11.920
If you dare to try

29:11.920 --> 29:13.440
any little tricks,

29:13.920 --> 29:14.790
I'll kill you.

29:15.550 --> 29:17.260
Thanks to your wise decision.

29:17.280 --> 29:20.330
There's no need for you to toil so much,
and we also get to eat.

29:20.330 --> 29:22.850
When do I start, Sirs?

29:23.400 --> 29:24.270
-Now.
-Now.

29:40.850 --> 29:42.850
There aren't too many people here,

29:43.030 --> 29:44.440
only about 30.

29:44.920 --> 29:46.630
Two guards at the cave entrance
over there,

29:46.630 --> 29:48.160
and another guard in front.

29:49.230 --> 29:50.560
Where does

29:50.720 --> 29:52.000
that path lead?

30:15.430 --> 30:16.880
Y-Your Excellency.

30:18.850 --> 30:20.890
Have you found anything?

30:21.550 --> 30:23.350
The location Zhu Luan mentioned

30:23.400 --> 30:24.600
should be right here.

30:25.250 --> 30:26.580
If I guess correctly,

30:27.320 --> 30:29.450
the Spirit Immortal Sect's lair
is just ahead.

30:29.450 --> 30:31.210
T-The lair?

30:32.590 --> 30:33.400
Charge!

30:35.260 --> 30:36.320
Don't be reckless.

30:37.770 --> 30:39.200
Now we have the map,

30:39.220 --> 30:40.820
but we still know nothing
about the locations

30:40.820 --> 30:42.350
of Tian Xing and the others.

30:42.510 --> 30:44.110
If we act recklessly,

30:44.130 --> 30:45.790
they will definitely act in desperation.

30:45.790 --> 30:47.200
T-T-Then we...

30:48.790 --> 30:51.000
What's your plan?

30:52.110 --> 30:54.170
Let's secure the surroundings first

30:54.680 --> 30:56.310
and wait for the right moment.

30:56.310 --> 30:56.920
Okay.

31:31.500 --> 31:32.690
Suyin,

31:32.720 --> 31:35.120
here is the medicine
and the map of the cave.

31:36.360 --> 31:38.120
Yun told me to tell you

31:38.150 --> 31:39.900
that she has arranged people outside,

31:39.900 --> 31:41.570
ready to back you up
to rescue people at any time.

31:41.570 --> 31:42.290
Okay.

31:43.670 --> 31:45.800
It's dangerous here. Go back quickly.

32:02.640 --> 32:03.640
Your Excellency.

32:04.500 --> 32:05.170
Fan Yun.

32:06.270 --> 32:07.000
You're here.

32:09.110 --> 32:10.110
Why is he here too?

32:11.230 --> 32:12.910
We met on the way.

32:14.030 --> 32:14.640
Really?

32:15.310 --> 32:15.880
Yes.

32:17.200 --> 32:17.640
It seems

32:17.640 --> 32:19.770
someone shamelessly followed along.

32:20.190 --> 32:21.360
What a tagalong.

32:21.890 --> 32:23.220
I'm here to accompany Fan Yun,

32:23.220 --> 32:25.010
not to participate in your operation.

32:25.010 --> 32:26.310
What do you mean by that?

32:26.310 --> 32:27.480
We have enough hands here.

32:27.480 --> 32:28.610
Who asked you to participate?

32:28.610 --> 32:30.470
-Besides...
-Alright. Alright.

32:30.770 --> 32:32.030
There are many civilians inside.

32:32.030 --> 32:33.820
One more person means more strength.

32:33.820 --> 32:35.880
Since he's here, let's act together.

32:44.340 --> 32:45.340
Your Excellency.

32:45.780 --> 32:46.570
Look.

32:46.600 --> 32:47.260
Come.

32:54.940 --> 32:56.270
-Go.
-Go.

33:20.940 --> 33:21.940
Still breathing.

33:22.830 --> 33:23.690
How about this?

33:23.710 --> 33:24.670
Lord Desheng,

33:24.690 --> 33:25.490
Gao Ran,

33:25.590 --> 33:26.400
you guys stay here

33:26.400 --> 33:27.500
and look after these civilians.

33:27.500 --> 33:28.700
The three of us will go in first.

33:28.700 --> 33:29.350
Okay.

33:29.870 --> 33:30.950
How about I go in?

33:31.110 --> 33:31.710
It's fine.

33:32.120 --> 33:33.180
As long as I'm here,

33:33.670 --> 33:35.060
I won't let Fan Yun get hurt.

33:35.060 --> 33:36.860
I will protect Fan Yun well, too.

33:38.960 --> 33:39.810
Gao Ran,

33:40.400 --> 33:41.930
be extra careful yourself.

33:46.570 --> 33:47.120
Yes.

33:59.050 --> 34:01.090
Can you two put some effort into it?

34:18.330 --> 34:18.920
Quick.

34:20.110 --> 34:20.969
I'm exhausted.

34:23.760 --> 34:24.820
What are you doing?

34:34.750 --> 34:36.520
I've finally seen someone alive.

34:36.520 --> 34:37.360
I just arrived.

34:37.360 --> 34:38.340
I got lost here.

34:38.360 --> 34:39.960
I thought I couldn't get out.

34:44.469 --> 34:45.469
I want to ask,

34:45.489 --> 34:48.949
how do I get to the Second Division
of the Spirit Immortal Sect?

34:58.710 --> 34:59.460
Thanks.

34:59.480 --> 35:02.010
You go ahead with your business.
I'm leaving.

35:04.030 --> 35:04.890
Go quickly. Go.

35:13.310 --> 35:14.190
Thanks!

35:21.810 --> 35:23.320
Good thing we met a fool.

35:32.400 --> 35:33.350
Your Excellency.

35:33.350 --> 35:34.060
Suyin.

35:37.400 --> 35:38.150
Suyin.

35:48.080 --> 35:48.940
Your Ladyship.

35:49.860 --> 35:51.120
No need to be so formal.

35:51.160 --> 35:53.090
I'm no longer the Governor's wife.

35:55.100 --> 35:56.900
Let's save the civilians first.

35:57.450 --> 35:58.260
Suyin.

35:58.290 --> 35:59.820
Are all the civilians here?

35:59.980 --> 36:01.650
There are more on the other side.

36:01.650 --> 36:02.850
More civilians?

36:04.230 --> 36:05.490
Should we save them or not?

36:05.490 --> 36:06.690
Of course, we should.

36:06.840 --> 36:07.470
Suyin.

36:07.740 --> 36:08.800
Where is Tian Xing?

36:08.940 --> 36:09.870
I'll go find him.

36:14.370 --> 36:15.210
Everyone,

36:15.230 --> 36:16.670
we are here to save you.

36:16.700 --> 36:17.710
Hurry and follow us.

36:17.710 --> 36:18.190
Come on.

36:18.660 --> 36:20.120
-Be careful.
-Be careful.

36:20.270 --> 36:20.860
Come on.

36:21.390 --> 36:21.920
Careful.

36:22.690 --> 36:23.620
-Come on.
-Slowly.

36:23.620 --> 36:24.230
Careful.

36:25.910 --> 36:27.840
-Keep up.
-Be careful.

36:29.280 --> 36:30.470
-Keep up.
-Here.

36:30.880 --> 36:31.680
Tian Xing.

36:32.260 --> 36:33.000
How are you doing?

36:33.000 --> 36:33.770
Suyin,

36:33.840 --> 36:34.670
what happened to Tian Xing?

36:34.670 --> 36:36.150
He was locked up
by the Spirit Immortal Sect.

36:36.150 --> 36:37.760
He must be very weak now.

36:37.810 --> 36:38.500
Suyin,

36:38.720 --> 36:40.270
take Tian Xing
and the civilians out first.

36:40.270 --> 36:41.320
Leave the rest to us.

36:41.320 --> 36:41.830
Okay.

36:41.930 --> 36:42.860
I'm not leaving.

36:43.810 --> 36:45.740
My sister's fate is still unknown.

36:46.070 --> 36:47.280
I must find her.

36:48.370 --> 36:49.890
But you have a fever.

36:50.510 --> 36:51.400
It's fine.

36:51.780 --> 36:53.440
If he wants to follow, let him.

36:53.800 --> 36:55.600
But if we encounter any danger later,

36:55.600 --> 36:57.130
just don't become a burden.

36:57.370 --> 36:59.090
Don't call Tian Xing a burden!

36:59.580 --> 37:01.540
Why? Can't handle the truth?

37:01.560 --> 37:03.190
If you can't speak nicely,
just shut up, okay?

37:03.190 --> 37:03.820
Exactly.

37:04.140 --> 37:04.930
Alright,

37:04.960 --> 37:06.120
stop arguing.

37:06.140 --> 37:07.710
Suyin, where are the rest

37:07.740 --> 37:08.590
of the civilians?

37:08.590 --> 37:09.330
Over there.

37:10.860 --> 37:13.060
Qi Zheng, take the civilians out first.

37:13.800 --> 37:14.510
Go quickly.

37:14.530 --> 37:15.300
Everyone,

37:15.510 --> 37:17.230
the Spirit Immortal Sect's
cave exit is straight ahead.

37:17.230 --> 37:18.070
You go out first.

37:18.070 --> 37:21.000
My Guardian Corps
is waiting for you at the entrance.

37:21.350 --> 37:22.030
Go. Go.

37:22.050 --> 37:23.300
Come on, careful.

37:42.040 --> 37:43.800
They trapped people in a place like this.

37:43.800 --> 37:45.130
No wonder they fell ill.

37:46.890 --> 37:48.370
Folks, get up quickly.

37:48.400 --> 37:49.800
Leave this place with us.

37:49.820 --> 37:50.620
That's right.

37:50.730 --> 37:51.940
We are here to save you.

37:51.940 --> 37:53.100
Hurry and follow us.

37:53.300 --> 37:55.660
You are that female official, Fan Yun?

37:55.690 --> 37:56.890
Yes, I am.

37:56.910 --> 37:58.910
We came to get everyone out.

37:58.940 --> 38:00.580
The Spirit Immortal Sect lied to us.

38:00.580 --> 38:02.250
They said they could cure the disease.

38:02.250 --> 38:03.000
But...

38:03.870 --> 38:05.510
they just left us here to die.

38:06.460 --> 38:07.190
Are you here

38:07.790 --> 38:09.150
trying to lie to us too?

38:09.800 --> 38:11.130
-I...
-If you stay here,

38:11.380 --> 38:13.010
your condition will only get worse.

38:13.010 --> 38:14.720
If there is any misunderstanding,

38:14.720 --> 38:16.280
we can talk about it after getting out.

38:16.280 --> 38:16.840
Yes.

38:16.840 --> 38:17.550
Please follow us quickly.

38:17.550 --> 38:18.680
Let's get out first.

38:19.000 --> 38:20.850
Why should I trust a little girl like you?
